{"tid":1431254,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[負能量]擺低形容依家心情嘅歌詞","createTime":"2019-08-08T02:57:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T09:10:36.000Z","uid":49869,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"a003e17dab017d982ee28cb63a98cce3d33664b7","tid":1431254,"uid":49869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:57:51.000Z","msg":"掌心因此多出一根刺<br />\n沒有刺痛便懶知<br />\n就當共你 有舊情沒有往事<br />\n<br />\n如煙 因給你遞過火<br />\n如火 卻也沒熔掉我<br />\n回望最初 當喪失是得著可不可<br />\n可痛若驪歌 樂如兒歌<br />\n像你沒來過 沒去過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"caa252cd970b8e37d7b63363188f25528d2a794a","tid":1431254,"uid":49869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:19:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1"},{"pid":"c292bd2a1fa5b5bd2c4c8b6d3c150627a19c8b2e","tid":1431254,"uid":190322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:23:06.000Z","msg":"I wear the black for the poor and the beaten down, livin' in the hopeless, hungry side of town<br />\n<br />\nI wear it for the sick and lonely old,<br />\nFor the reckless ones whose bad trip left them cold,<br />\nI wear the black in mournin' for the lives that could have been,<br />\nEach week we lose a hundred fine young men.<br />\n<br />\n-Johnny Cash"},{"pid":"0357fc72aff723ddb83b56e2f49d757305b021ae","tid":1431254,"uid":299371,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:27:27.000Z","msg":"無謂再關心你 我沒資格慰問你<br />\n無謂再騷擾你 我沒這塊厚面皮"},{"pid":"f8f8c1d8022b2ff67c3a03e9a781cef4fe6166b4","tid":1431254,"uid":49869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:30:14.000Z","msg":"一想起再累也是要做人<br />\n我的思緒便繃緊"},{"pid":"703819f2acd38447beb94905da73d3718e173ef5","tid":1431254,"uid":265027,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:48:59.000Z","msg":"FUCK THE POPO 我屌你老母<br />\nFUCK THE POPO 我屌你老母"},{"pid":"6d9b62d0d834fad14d0a6ab33cb13d813ac5eba6","tid":1431254,"uid":234219,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:57:22.000Z","msg":"能不能繼續 對我哭 對我笑 對我好<br />\n繼續讓我 為你想 為你瘋 陪你老<br />\n你好不好 好想知道<br />\n別急著把回憶都丟掉<br />\n<br />\n我只需要你在身邊 陪我吵 陪我鬧<br />\n用好的我 把過去壞的我 都換掉<br />\n好想聽到 你堅決說愛我<br />\n可惜回不去那一秒<br />\n你，好不好？"},{"pid":"4394dea2f8fbb85723e1a3f33f1aba69f44aaf90","tid":1431254,"uid":276758,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:04:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">風雨總會停 亂世變太平<br />\n有我共你一起見證</span><br />\n<br />\n都不緊要 跌碰總少不了<br />\n要看開些少<br />\n不快要大叫 樂共苦差很少<br />\n扭轉兩者只需數秒<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">新聞 又報導誰輕生<br />\n誰沒信心 困境之中鬥爭<br />\n若放棄當個人 真的太笨<br />\n怎可作不必要犧牲<br />\n<br />\n走得過癮 剩低幾個傷心<br />\n如若你肯 似金剛般變身<br />\n面對滿天責任 打不死摔不跌踩不沉<br />\n重拾你 身份</span>"},{"pid":"1c76cfa94d4e6df4263a464388d0441f56cf4b09","tid":1431254,"uid":49869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:03:26.000Z","msg":"回味著妳昨晚像惡夢似的話<br />\n妳給我的竟不是愛情<br />\n<br />\n是妳說從來無人像我在做盡傻事<br />\n竟然仍然認真對這玩意<br />\n為何從前愛得極度容易<br />\n將來和誰再講這段趣事<br />\n<br />\n纏綿遊戲過後 為何能捨得放手<br />\n是定律或是愛不夠<br />\n告訴我這段纏綿遊戲過後<br />\n為何情不可永久<br />\n是事實並沒有真愛 或根本我未看透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e79f6cd4c8fc8efb799faa3e6b94c49350cb96","tid":1431254,"uid":278836,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:07:17.000Z","msg":"要是 彼此都有些 既定路程<br />\n學會灑脫 好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dfa051c76add6c834b95bb72d1ce17f803adf12","tid":1431254,"uid":125976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:27:26.000Z","msg":"人人親近我 無人爭奪我<br />\n無人關懷是誰大平賣親和<br />\n平凡像我路過 十個似我<br />\n情敵實在太多<br />\n天都不理我 令我想清楚<br />\n感情是來自由弱者所寫的悲歌<br />\n事實上為什麼不拍到拖<br />\n說穿了我不美<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4474dbb981e8184b01eecd2d0b4dc3b0d581636d","tid":1431254,"uid":209947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:39:40.000Z","msg":"還未捨得不痛心　怕刻骨不銘心<br />\n在記憶裡愛　不痛不真<br />\n嫌受傷得不夠深　刺青刻得更深<br />\n樂意忍　就忍到無憾<br />\n誓要你　成就我愛到不像是凡人"},{"pid":"903f3a9a5a4315548e4d0426e968b0c6923ab545","tid":1431254,"uid":288513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:47:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PdB0oYB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPdB0oYB.png&h=a0f5c8a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c892f9e6670e199efd86c2b251ff9eb2cdb9322d","tid":1431254,"uid":57895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:49:34.000Z","msg":"不快樂怪誰 失散後隨便活過去"},{"pid":"89375bb186534303cedc9ef4c08765a2b8d7e5da","tid":1431254,"uid":132579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:51:55.000Z","msg":"人人都怕難 怕倦 怕撲空"},{"pid":"22b38b610161d87d57521b906b0d52de0d220560","tid":1431254,"uid":152252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:03:21.000Z","msg":"沒結果的花　未完成的牽掛<br />\n我們學會許多說法來掩飾不碰的傷疤<br />\n<br />\n因為我會想起你我害怕面對自己<br />\n我的意志總被寂寞吞食<br />\n<br />\n因為你總會提醒過去總不會過去<br />\n有種真愛不是我的"},{"pid":"5ab31293ad323565094dcccaf2f6936fb065ad7b","tid":1431254,"uid":266336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:05:05.000Z","msg":"就算在昨天高高低低每一篇 你我原來怎麼蛻變<br />\n總可躍進動盪時局裡 緊守這片天<br />\n這巨輪 又再一天一天轉<br />\n我們未可回歸到美麗從前 亦有新經典上演<br />\n就算在某天風急花飛再一篇 你我仍然甘於應戰<br />\n走得過最絕望危難了 哪會怕考驗<br />\n時代變 人物風景都改變<br />\n我們英勇卻未輸從前 如常在苦困裡彰顯 未會變<br />\n<br />\n無人可以 叫巨輪停下半秒<br />\n良心發現 可否再讓我開始<br />\n但天可有半點公義<br />\n如何可將它扭轉 抵不過隻手遮天<br />\n誰可改變 叫巨輪停下半秒<br />\n良心發現 這黑暗會否終止<br />\n越轉越糊塗越錯亂<br />\n今天轉身已是太遲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cis3naW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCis3naW.png&h=a5149bb8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c8d4e276a5a6e394a20055f660d76144bf1543","tid":1431254,"uid":166591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:41:46.000Z","msg":"Now I can&rsquo;t think of air without thinking of you"},{"pid":"6b9a1f4521b56fd9ba37e87193a58f71985774ef","tid":1431254,"uid":209947,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T22:03:54.000Z","msg":"想愛但愛誰 搜索著留戀的證據 先知跌得多碎"},{"pid":"38562f152ce0968f97cd70539a971a9d7592e3c0","tid":1431254,"uid":185316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T23:04:39.000Z","msg":"多麼蠢的蠢豬 個個也來揶揄<br />\n充當不起公主 並沒段段艷遇<br />\n悠然面對這悲劇遭遇<br />\n齊集給了你當笑話書<br />\n多麼蠢的蠢豬 那勝過條人魚<br />\n即使爭都爭輸 仍然從未怪罪於天主<br />\n就當戀愛運很特殊<br />\n期望你前來叫我蠢豬 講愛情暗語"},{"pid":"65fdc910f0291b217e4be7f6149c9b1c2e2f87fd","tid":1431254,"uid":49869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:31:43.000Z","msg":"明明在轉彎 你一叫 就馬上回頭<br />\n為何還在等 也沒人 求我別要走<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a5f66b9bfb0ba6b0e12bcfda3d81691388fe67","tid":1431254,"uid":191555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:53:02.000Z","msg":"Wake me up, before you go"},{"pid":"5dac36731a99215777db42623ee14d952d3ce2f0","tid":1431254,"uid":222251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:02:58.000Z","msg":"我就放開手 無謂再忍你<br />\n明白放過你是放過自己這個道理"},{"pid":"87665dd643ae0a2a7ee6dc609cb123c04c998a12","tid":1431254,"uid":49869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:30:30.000Z","msg":"傷我或是害我都慘不過 教我記得一起幸福過<br />\n情願我聽不清楚 當時誰人口口聲聲不會掉低我<br />\n待我差我沒有奈何 為何扮好心慰問很掛念我麼<br />\n還能成為蜜友麼 <br />\n你說得真輕鬆 講笑也別太過"},{"pid":"3dfafd460a0815f56c41f0ea06f8d22c07f98587","tid":1431254,"uid":198837,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:57:32.000Z","msg":"朋友是 朋友吧<br />\n和你身份不進化<br />\n也許這一世都這樣嗎<br />\n<br />\n如果你愛他 沒說話<br />\n我等你某天出嫁<br />\n然後我送上賀吻<br />\n親密無奈最多一剎那<br />\n<br />\n難道你到八十歲至收我的花<br />\n<br />\n情侶是 情侶吧<br />\n難以將身份降價<br />\n你好心婉拒不傷大雅"},{"pid":"0d00fd3eb75ad094c2c9600c6c078fb61ca29e74","tid":1431254,"uid":304344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:07:04.000Z","msg":"就這樣 就這樣<br />\n怕真相 太難看<br />\n我想對愛情還抱有希望<br />\n我們倆 就這樣<br />\n<br />\n以為能夠功德圓滿 最後勉強好聚好散<br />\n一段感情這樣收場 你也會 遺憾<br />\n<br />\n（李榮浩 就這樣）"},{"pid":"055442e2b7d974eb4cc848a72b8f61e168628504","tid":1431254,"uid":263086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:10:43.000Z","msg":"我知道潮落之後一定有潮起 我不能忘記"},{"pid":"816c1e7cf180b7f47a6bfa33fb03860663653360","tid":1431254,"uid":49869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:55:36.000Z","msg":"最希冀的那一個 心儀這一個<br />\n<br />\n尋尋找找為何都找不到 為何有無盡孤苦的單數<br />\n合意的 永遠最難擁抱 未見到答案的傾慕<br />\n和伴侶無奈永遠差半步"},{"pid":"2f88fb3bf5800a3062c0346b35489992ee132a3d","tid":1431254,"uid":138361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:24:57.000Z","msg":"成班失戀歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6694d70aecb6d7967cabc4100c92c156ae3b99a","tid":1431254,"uid":49869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:47:45.000Z","msg":"值得不值得　把你去永遠記著<br />\n你把我腦袋裡的回憶全都壞了"},{"pid":"9e7abcdb7628a1bb860e760417838d4aaf864412","tid":1431254,"uid":183887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T21:43:56.000Z","msg":"改天我又覺悲傷 早失方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />向"},{"pid":"1a5bdfd9e80771ebf2ac5dc39de50e21ff2b4930","tid":1431254,"uid":3852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T21:50:54.000Z","msg":"這時期演傷心戲 戲爛人未死"},{"pid":"bc6dccdfc412c8f07697a9180504a821a7238440","tid":1431254,"uid":211727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T21:54:00.000Z","msg":"明日の道は 止められない"},{"pid":"07863933e60f14e8176faf9f1e88fa17c6ca9dde","tid":1431254,"uid":167441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T21:55:43.000Z","msg":"When you try your best but you don't succeed <br />\nWhen you get what you want but not what you need <br />\nWhen you feel so tired but you can't sleep <br />\nStuck in reverse"},{"pid":"ac367efc0f6d306ed3c3193367a9ba4799bed640","tid":1431254,"uid":55177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:06:17.000Z","msg":"Slow down you crazy child<br />\nTake the phone off the hook and disappear for a while<br />\nIt's alright, you can afford to lose a day or two<br />\nWhen will you realize, Vienna waits for you?<br />\n<br />\nBilly Joel - Vienna"},{"pid":"42fa241f4950166de47293d002a577d975e1741c","tid":1431254,"uid":105363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:24:08.000Z","msg":"相見是意外 見不到才是應該<br />\n我本可以分得開 看得開"},{"pid":"a9cb43ac7f8fc1b044c237aba24b612bd2387105","tid":1431254,"uid":22984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:15:23.000Z","msg":"傷我或是害我都慘不過　<br />\n教我記得一起幸福過<br />\n情願我聽不清楚　<br />\n當時誰人口口聲聲不會掉低我<br />\n待我差我沒有奈何　<br />\n為何扮好心慰問很掛念我麼<br />\n還能成為蜜友麼　你說得真輕鬆<br />\n講笑也　別太過"},{"pid":"c682fae0451541a823255089c4daa7cf93f3662a","tid":1431254,"uid":228946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:31:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c3f62d5e0ff8e29783b3cf5eb6f3692ab5170d3","tid":1431254,"uid":209947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:04:22.000Z","msg":"明明你也最愛我 沒理由愛不到結果<br />\n只要你敢不懦弱 憑什麼我們要錯過<br />\n<br />\n真係好掛住你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652aae5319b41a6d8e12c81c5a91e7bca6f7ab56","tid":1431254,"uid":288071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0