y<br />\nYou're the King of these people<br />\nYou're the Lord of this nation<br />\nYou are<br />\nYou're the light in this darkness<br />\nYou're the hope to the hopeless<br />\nYou're the peace to the restless<br />\nYou are<br />\nThere is no one like our God<br />\nThere is no one like our God<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">For greater things have yet to come<br />\nAnd greater things are still to be done in this city<br />\nGreater things have yet to come<br />\nAnd greater things are still to be done in this city</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03e219821524f216c105531518030136248f22c","tid":1431254,"uid":200098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:52:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}